# A股量化因子工厂 · 功能流程图

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    %% Entry
    START([系统启动]) --> INIT[初始化]
    INIT --> LOAD_CONFIG[加载配置]
    LOAD_CONFIG --> INIT_DB[初始化DuckDB]
    INIT_DB --> INIT_SCHEDULER[初始化调度器]
    INIT_SCHEDULER --> WAIT_T1{等待定时任务}
    
    %% Data Pipeline
    WAIT_T1 -->|00:00 数据更新| DATA_UPDATE[下载最新行情]
    DATA_UPDATE --> FETCH_DAILY[日线数据]
    FETCH_DAILY --> FETCH_FIN[财务数据]
    FETCH_FIN --> FETCH_HKT[北向资金]
    FETCH_HKT --> STORE_DUCK[存储到DuckDB]
    STORE_DUCK --> DATA_DONE[数据更新完成]
    
    %% Factor Mining Pipeline
    DATA_DONE -->|01:00 因子挖掘| MINER_START[启动因子挖掘]
    MINER_START --> GEN_TECH[技术因子候选]
    GEN_TECH --> GEN_FUND[基本面因子候选]
    GEN_FUND --> GEN_CROSS[量价交叉因子候选]
    GEN_CROSS --> GEN_COMPOSITE[复合因子候选]
    
    GEN_TECH --> MERGE_CAND[合并候选因子]
    GEN_FUND --> MERGE_CAND
    GEN_CROSS --> MERGE_CAND
    GEN_COMPOSITE --> MERGE_CAND
    
    MERGE_CAND --> CALC_FACTORS[批量计算因子值]
    CALC_FACTORS --> EVAL_IC{评估IC}
    EVAL_IC -->|IC < 0.02| REJECT_FACTOR[淘汰因子]
    EVAL_IC -->|IC >= 0.02| EVAL_IR{评估IR}
    EVAL_IR -->|IR < 0.3| REJECT_FACTOR
    EVAL_IR -->|IR >= 0.3| ADD_POOL[进入因子池]
    
    REJECT_FACTOR --> DISCARD
    ADD_POOL --> POOL_UPDATE[因子池更新]
    
    %% Factor Evaluation
    POOL_UPDATE -->|03:00 因子评估| EVAL_ALL[评估所有因子]
    EVAL_ALL --> CALC_IC_IR[计算IC/IR序列]
    CALC_IC_IR --> GROUP_TEST[分组回测]
    GROUP_TEST --> DECAY_TEST[衰减分析]
    DECAY_TEST --> RANK_POOL[因子池重排]
    RANK_POOL --> APPLY_RULES{优胜劣汰}
    
    APPLY_RULES -->|IR > 1.0| PROMOTE[⭐升级-核心因子]
    APPLY_RULES -->|IR > 0.5| KEEP[✅保留-可用因子]
    APPLY_RULES -->|IR > 0.3| DEMOTE[🔶降级-观察因子]
    APPLY_RULES -->|IR < 0.3| EVICT[❌淘汰出池]
    
    PROMOTE --> POOL_DONE
    KEEP --> POOL_DONE
    DEMOTE --> POOL_DONE
    EVICT --> POOL_DONE
    
    %% Strategy Generation
    POOL_DONE -->|05:00 策略生成| SELECT_FACTORS[选取Top因子]
    SELECT_FACTORS --> BUILD_SIGNALS[构建信号模板]
    BUILD_SIGNALS --> GEN_PARAMS[参数空间生成]
    GEN_PARAMS --> OPTIMIZE_PARAMS[参数优化]
    OPTIMIZE_PARAMS --> GEN_STRATEGIES[生成策略候选]
    
    %% Backtest
    GEN_STRATEGIES -->|07:00 全市场回测| BT_SETUP[回测准备]
    BT_SETUP --> LOAD_STOCKS[加载主板股票]
    LOAD_STOCKS --> GET_DATA[获取历史数据]
    GET_DATA --> RUN_BACKTEST[逐日回测]
    
    RUN_BACKTEST --> FOR_EACH_DAY{遍历每日}
    FOR_EACH_DAY -->|有数据| CHECK_SIGNALS[检查信号]
    CHECK_SIGNALS -->|有信号| GEN_ORDERS[生成订单]
    CHECK_SIGNALS -->|无信号| NEXT_D
    
    GEN_ORDERS --> RISK_CHECK[风控检查]
    RISK_CHECK -->|通过| EXEC_ORDER[执行订单]
    RISK_CHECK -->|失败| SKIP[跳过]
    
    EXEC_ORDER --> UPDATE_POS[更新持仓]
    SKIP --> NEXT_D
    UPDATE_POS --> CALC_PNL[计算盈亏]
    CALC_PNL --> NEXT_D
    
    NEXT_D[下一日] --> FOR_EACH_DAY
    FOR_EACH_DAY -->|完成| CALC_PERF[计算绩效]
    
    %% Performance Analysis
    CALC_PERF --> CALC_SHARPE[夏普比率]
    CALC_PERF --> CALC_MDD[最大回撤]
    CALC_PERF --> CALC_WINRATE[胜率/盈亏比]
    CALC_SHARPE --> RANK_STRAT[策略排名]
    CALC_MDD --> RANK_STRAT
    CALC_WINRATE --> RANK_STRAT
    
    RANK_STRAT -->|Sharpe > 1.5| PROMOTE_STRAT[🚀实盘候选]
    RANK_STRAT -->|Sharpe > 1.0| KEEP_STRAT[📈模拟跟踪]
    RANK_STRAT -->|Sharpe > 0.5| ARCHIVE_STRAT[📝存档观察]
    RANK_STRAT -->|Sharpe < 0.5| EVICT_STRAT[🗑️淘汰]
    
    %% Report & Alert
    PROMOTE_STRAT --> REPORT
    KEEP_STRAT --> REPORT
    ARCHIVE_STRAT --> REPORT
    EVICT_STRAT --> REPORT
    
    REPORT -->|15:30 日报| GEN_HTML[生成HTML报告]
    GEN_HTML --> GEN_TRADES_CSV[交易明细CSV]
    GEN_TRADES_CSV --> GEN_DAILY_SUMMARY[每日总结]
    
    GEN_DAILY_SUMMARY -->|18:00| REBALANCE_POOL[因子池再平衡]
    REBALANCE_POOL --> WAIT_T2{等待下一轮}
    
    WAIT_T2 -->|次日00:00| DATA_UPDATE
    
    %% Alerter
    ALERT_TRIGGER{告警触发}
    ALERT_TRIGGER -->|因子池异常| SEND_FEISHU[飞书通知]
    ALERT_TRIGGER -->|策略亏损超限| SEND_FEISHU
    ALERT_TRIGGER -->|数据获取失败| SEND_FEISHU
    
    %% Loop
    WAIT_T1 -.->|循环| DATA_UPDATE
    WAIT_T2 -.->|7×24循环| DATA_UPDATE
    
    %% Legend
    subgraph 图例
        A[矩形=处理步骤] --> B{菱形=判断分支}
        C[六边形=结果] --> D[/平行四边形=输入输出/]
    end
```

