## 核心循环时序

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Sched as Scheduler
    participant Miner as FactorMiner
    participant Eval as FactorEval
    participant Pool as FactorPool
    participant Gen as StrategyGen
    participant Opt as Optimizer
    participant BT as Backtester
    participant Perf as Performance
    participant DB as DuckDB
    participant Alert as Alerter

    Note over Sched: 7×24 全天候运转

    Sched->>Miner: 01:00 触发
    Miner->>DB: 读取原始数据
    DB-->>Miner: 价量/财务/北向
    Miner->>Miner: 挖掘100个候选因子
    Miner->>Eval: 提交候选

    Sched->>Eval: 03:00 触发
    Eval->>DB: 读取历史数据
    Eval->>Eval: IC/IR分析
    Eval->>Eval: 分组回测
    Eval->>Eval: 衰减测试
    Eval-->>Pool: 评估结果

    Sched->>Pool: 18:00 触发
    Pool->>Pool: 排名更新
    Pool->>Pool: 淘汰 IR<0.3
    Pool->>Pool: 晋升 IR>1.0

    Sched->>Gen: 05:00 触发
    Gen->>Pool: 读取Top因子
    Gen->>Gen: 生成策略模板
    Gen->>Opt: 提交优化任务
    Opt->>BT: 批量回测
    BT-->>Opt: 回测结果
    Opt-->>Gen: 最优参数

    Sched->>BT: 07:00 触发
    BT->>DB: 加载3200只主板股
    loop 每日回测
        BT->>BT: 信号→风控→成交
        BT->>DB: 记录交易
    end
    BT-->>Perf: 交易明细
    Perf->>Perf: 计算绩效
    Perf->>DB: 存储结果

    Sched->>Perf: 15:30 触发
    Perf->>Perf: 生成HTML报告
    Perf-->>Alert: 发送日报

    Alert->>Alert: 监控异常
    Alert->>Alert: 飞书通知
```
